      *
      * PFOPSR - Midas / OPICS Interface  Subroutine                  *
      *                                                               *
      * Called by: Main                                               *
      *                                                               *
      * Calls: None                                                   *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C     PFOPSR        BEGSR
      *
     C***********          READ SDOPINPD                 76                                   JMI111
     C                   READ      XXOPINPD                               76                  JMI111
     C     *IN76         IFEQ      '1'
     C                   MOVE      60            N                              **************
     C                   EXSR      DBERR                                        *     60     *
     C                   GOTO      ENDT                                         **************
     C                   ENDIF
      *
     C     P@MODE        IFNE      'A'
     C     P@MODE        OREQ      'A'
     C     OPLCD         ANDEQ     WURDNB
      *
      ** Convert Last Change Date, Day Number, To DDMMMYY Format.
     C                   Z-ADD     OPLCD         ZDAYNO
     C                   EXSR      ZDATE2
     C                   MOVE      ZADATE        LCDA              7
     C                   MOVE      ZADATE        WULCD             7
      *
      ** Determine Last Change Type.
     C     OPTYLC        IFEQ      'A'
     C                   MOVE      'Amend '      WUCHTP
     C                   ELSE
     C                   MOVE      'Insert'      WUCHTP
     C                   END
      *
      ** Print Midas/OPICS  Interface Data Page.
     C                   WRITE     ICDHDR
     C                   WRITE     PFOPRCD
      *
     C     NROF          ADD       1             NROF
      *
     C                   ENDIF
      *
     C     ZPFOP         ENDSR
      *
